name: Cynet Circuit
text: Target 1 "Firewall" Link Monster you control; Special Summon any number of monsters from your GY to either field so they are linked to it. If your LP are 2000 or less: You can banish this card from your GY; return 1 "Firewall" Link Monster from your GY to the Extra Deck, then you can Special Summon it from your Extra Deck. You can only use each effect of "Cynet Circuit" once per turn.
